ygData.msgSnippet: Here is the message I got from the person who told me of this weapon when I asked him more about it... ... Supposdly, the swords spell effect is something like
ygData.messageBody:
Here is the message I got from the person who told me of this weapon when I
asked him more about it...

>I decided to hold off on telling people where to find
>it because it is still so rare and I thought I'd give
>people a chance to discover its whereabouts.
>
>You do have to fight through a group of level 50's
>and then get really lucky on your loot to aquire
>this badboy though.
>
>BTW, very nice list of items.
>
>-Macaw
>

Supposdly, the swords spell effect is something like a 170 direct damage
spell, in addition to it being a real nice weapon...





----- Original Message -----
From: Greg Gillan <GGillan@...>
To: <eqbards@onelist.com>
Sent: Monday, June 28, 1999 15:44
Subject: [eqbards] Short Sword of the Ykesha


> From: Greg Gillan <GGillan@...>
>
> Sorry, not bard specific, but since 99% of bards use 1h slashing, thought
> you might be interested.
> This weapon was just posted up on Gameznet. Does anyone know where to
find
> it? How hard it is to get? I'm sure its not something that I'll be able
to
> obtain myself, but it would be nice to know.
> http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/ykesha.html
>
>
> Elwyn
> Level 22 Bard
> Erollosi Marr
>
>
